name: TERIMA KASIH (THANK YOU)
description:
“...Terima Kasih
Yang tlah berjuang di hari ini
Esok pagi
Kita bertempur lagi...”

Sorry, Please, and Thank You, three words that will save our lives.
Thank yous for keep fighting.

Lyrics and Performance by Riko Prayitno & Prjct Mncrgkn, twitter @rikoprayitn0
